<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DT TRAVEL - Layanan Transportasi Premium & Eksekutif</title>
    
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #0f172a;
        }
        /* Navbar Styling */
        .custom-navbar {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.8);
        }
        .nav-link {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: #475569 !important;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }
        .nav-link:hover {
            color: #1d4ed8 !important;
        }
        /* Hero Styling */
        .hero-section {
            position: relative;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9) 0%, rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.85) 100%), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544620347-c4fd4a3d5957?q=80&w=1200') no-repeat center center/cover;
            min-height: 70vh;
        }
        /* Card & Section Styling */
        .promo-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .promo-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .testi-card {
            border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.8);
            border-radius: 16px;
            background: #ffffff;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .testi-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) !important;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #0f172a;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light custom-navbar sticky-top py-3 shadow-sm">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-extrabold text-dark tracking-wider" href="/" style="font-size: 1.4rem;">DT TRAVEL</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#dtNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="dtNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto fw-bold text-uppercase gap-2 align-items-center">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link px-3" href="/">Beranda</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link px-3" href="/layanan">Layanan</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link px-3" href="/rute">Rute</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link px-3" href="/armada">Armada</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="btn btn-primary btn-sm px-4 text-white shadow-sm ms-2 rounded-3 py-2" href="/pemesanan">Pesan Sekarang</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm px-3 ms-1 rounded-3 py-2" href="/login">Admin</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero-section text-center text-white d-flex align-items-center">
        <div class="container py-5">
            <span class="badge bg-primary px-3 py-2 rounded-pill fw-semibold mb-3 text-uppercase tracking-wider" style="font-size: 0.8rem;">Premium Service</span>
            <h1 class="display-2 fw-extrabold tracking-tight mb-3" style="letter-spacing: -1px;">DT TRAVEL</h1>
            <p class="lead text-light mb-5 mx-auto" style="max-width: 600px; font-size: 1.25rem; opacity: 0.9;">
                "Perjalanan Nyaman, Aman, dan Tepat Waktu Bersama DT TRAVEL"
            </p>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3">
                <a href="/pemesanan" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-5 fw-bold shadow-lg py-3 rounded-3">Booking Tiket</a>
                <a href="/rute" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg px-5 fw-bold py-3 rounded-3">Jelajahi Rute</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container my-5 py-4">
        
        <% if (dataPromo) { %>
            <div class="card promo-card text-white p-5 shadow-lg mb-5 text-center">
                <div class="card-body py-3">
                    <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark px-3 py-2 rounded-pill fw-bold mb-3">PENAWARAN TERBATAS</span>
                    <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-2 text-uppercase">🔥 DISCOUNT <%= dataPromo.diskon_persen %>% OFF!</h2>
                    <p class="lead small mx-auto mb-4" style="max-width: 650px; opacity: 0.85;"><%= dataPromo.syarat_ketentuan %></p>
                    <a href="/pemesanan" class="btn btn-light btn-lg text-primary fw-bold px-5 py-2.5 rounded-3 shadow">Klaim Promo Sekarang</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <span class="text-primary fw-bold text-uppercase tracking-widest small">Testimonial</span>
            <h2 class="fw-extrabold text-dark mt-1">APA KATA MEREKA?</h2>
            <p class="text-muted small">Ulasan jujur dari pelanggan setia yang puas menikmati armada premium kami.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center">
            <% if (dataTestimoni.length === 0) { %>
                <div class="col-12 text-center text-muted py-4">
                    <p class="small">Belum ada ulasan testimoni di dalam database.</p>
                </div>
            <% } else { %>
                <% dataTestimoni.forEach(t => { %>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="card p-4 border-0 shadow-sm testi-card h-100 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                            <div class="mb-4">
                                <div class="text-warning mb-3 fs-5">★★★★★</div>
                                <p class="text-secondary lh-lg mb-0" style="font-size: 0.95rem; font-style: italic;">
                                    "<%= t.pesan_kesan %>"
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <hr class="opacity-10 my-3">
                                <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1 text-dark"><%= t.nama_pelanggan %></h6>
                                <span class="text-primary small fw-medium">Asal: <%= t.asal_kota %></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }) %>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="text-white pt-5 pb-4 mt-5">
        <div class="container text-center text-md-start">
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold text-warning mb-3">DT TRAVEL</h5>
                    <p class="small text-white-50">Platform eksklusif transportasi eksekutif antar kota dengan jaminan kenyamanan bintang lima serta layanan prima tepat waktu.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold text-warning mb-3">SISTEM NAVIGASI</h5>
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3 small">
                        <a href="/layanan" class="text-white-50 text-decoration-none">Layanan</a>
                        <a href="/rute" class="text-white-50 text-decoration-none">Rute Populer</a>
                        <a href="/armada" class="text-white-50 text-decoration-none">Armada</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 text-md-end text-center">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold text-warning mb-3">OFFICIAL OFFICE</h5>
                    <p class="small mb-1 text-white-50">📞 WhatsApp: 0812-XXXX-XXXX</p>
                    <p class="small mb-0 text-white-50">✉️ Email: info@dttravel.com</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr class="my-4 rgba(255,255,255,0.1)">
            <p class="text-center small text-white-50 mb-0">&copy; 2026 DT TRAVEL. Premium Service All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script